      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used under a validated SQA plan with documented regression test suite (1,847 benchmark cases), version-controlled input decks under Git, and formal change-control procedures. SQA plan reviewed and approved by quality engineering. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
