      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mesh convergence study must demonstrate QoI change < 2% between successive refinements; Richardson extrapolation reported.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed: coarse (142k elements), medium (387k elements), fine (1.02M elements). Stiffness QoI changed 4.1% coarse-to-medium and 0.8% medium-to-fine. Richardson extrapolation GCI = 1.3%. Fine mesh adopted for all production runs."
    },
